so i just came back from lauras house...we had a blast as usual. atlike 10:30 we walked into town, stopped by bizz's...which she wasn't expecting, and then we walked back to her house after eating a brownie thingy. she's leaving tommorrow...goin with her parents on vaca. right now she's at the beach with Ari, Lorenzo and possibly Will...i wanted to go with her soooo badly, as did she, however i promised my uncle that i'd be here for my cousin. (its her birthday party today, she's 4 and the cutest kid i've ever seen...so i can't say no.) it was like...the only chance i had to go to the beach this summer....which blows. but i promised next time that i'd come!!!
anyway, for labor day weekend, laura is going to come and stay over my house cuz her parents are going away. plus our concert is sometime during...then. heh. can't wait!
let's see...what else...? well my dad is going to be doing something with me on wed. he hasn't told me what. *shrug* probably another broadway play...which is always great! so far i've seen dracula, wicked, chitty chitty bang bang, x-mas show....and im probably missing one. i really wanna see the phantom of the opera. lalalala
